1
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:33,947
[Episode 3]

2
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:42,720
Dad.

3
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:45,280
Dad.

4
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,399
Dad.

5
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,959
Dad.

6
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:16,959
- Save him!
- Stop rushing me.

7
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:21,119
Hurry up!

8
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:26,680
Chu San, who exactly is this person?

9
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,719
This is a gunshot wound!

10
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:29,479
- Are you hurt?
- I'm fine.

11
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:31,320
Hurry up and save him, Dad!

12
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,879
The angle of this bullet is tricky.

13
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:53,080
My presbyopia is making it hard to see clearly.

14
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:55,759
How about you help him take it out?

15
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,759
I...

16
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,599
Saving him is more important! Hurry up!

17
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,800
Give it to me! Hurry up!

18
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,360
Be quick!

19
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,439
Come on!

20
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,199
Find it first.

21
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,480
Disinfection.

22
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,240
Dad.

23
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,520
It's okay. Take a deep breath.

24
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,280
Deep breaths.

25
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,599
You need to push the tweezers

26
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,680
all the way to the bottom in one go.

27
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:54,039
When you feel it touch the bullet,

28
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,319
immediately squeeze it tight

29
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,520
and pull it out quickly.

30
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,240
Be quick and decisive.

31
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,319
We can't worsen the wound.

32
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,600
Hurry up.

33
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,559
Pull it out.

34
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,040
Stop the bleeding.

35
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,360
All done.

36
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:49,319
How did you get involved with such a person?

37
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:52,119
And you brought him home?

38
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:57,399
He saved me before.

39
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:58,600
What happened to you?

40
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,399
He saved you?

41
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:03,519
I was robbed before.

42
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:05,600
He chased them away.

43
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,839
I already told you before.

44
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,800
Just give robbers the money.

45
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,920
Dad.

46
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:16,559
Didn't you teach me to repay kindness?

47
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,319
I've done everything I can.

48
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:23,800
Next, we'll see if this little brat

49
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:25,639
is tough enough to survive.

50
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:28,120
The triads.

51
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,920
They're all debt collectors.

52
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,319
You should rest early, too.

53
00:06:18,319 --> 00:06:21,079
Aren't you the mighty Dual Blades Xia?

54
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,520
How did you end up like this?

55
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:14,879
Chu San, he still hasn't woken up?

56
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,119
No.

57
00:09:19,099 --> 00:09:21,961
[He Chu San]

58
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,400
This damn kid.

59
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:32,880
Wild horse splitting its mane.

60
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:36,879
Your horse stance has to be firm.

61
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:38,360
Right.

62
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,200
Good. Next move.

63
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,759
Listen up!

64
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:44,000
White crane spreads its wings.

65
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:47,399
Raise your hands higher.

66
00:09:47,399 --> 00:09:49,000
Right.

67
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,040
This is it.

68
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,720
Don't wobble your legs.

69
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,840
Good, now continue.

70
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:56,520
Wave your hands like playing the lute.

71
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,960
Good.

72
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,800
Next move.

73
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,839
Come on, keep going.

74
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,279
Focus, stop looking around.

75
00:10:12,279 --> 00:10:13,480
Master, you can go on.

76
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,759
I have to get to school.

77
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,280
All right.

78
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,559
You're awake.

79
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,959
How do you feel?

80
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:41,480
What exactly happened?

81
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:43,400
How did you get hurt like this?

82
00:10:49,639 --> 00:10:51,919
Where are Xiao Ma and the others?

83
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,520
And your sister?

84
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,280
Beef tripe.

85
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,839
I want beef tripe.

86
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,199
Okay.

87
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,559
- Is it ready, Fei?
- Coming right up, I'll serve it to you.

88
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:46,480
I'll beat you to death.

89
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,559
Let's go.

90
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:50,039
Seen this person before?

91
00:11:50,039 --> 00:11:51,400
No.

92
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,080
Fei, hurry up!

93
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,880
Seen this person before?

94
00:11:58,039 --> 00:11:59,320
- No.
- Look carefully.

95
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,279
- Never seen him.
- Really?

96
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:03,279
- No.
- Fucking hell.

97
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:04,960
Your dad had cancer back then.

98
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:06,759
Your mom went door to door begging for money.

99
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:08,799
We spent money and effort to help.

100
00:12:08,799 --> 00:12:10,039
Now you're acting all high and mighty.

101
00:12:10,039 --> 00:12:11,399
Trying to show off, huh?

102
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:13,399
Ask your dad's spirit in heaven
if he recognizes you.

103
00:12:13,399 --> 00:12:14,840
You bitch, what did you say?

104
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,280
Come on, say it! Say it!

105
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:18,759
What did you say? Say it louder!

106
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,960
She'll never let go of that few bucks.

107
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,159
- Exactly.
- No wonder you're poor.

108
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,240
Say it louder, come on!

109
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,760
Come on, let's go.

110
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:45,639
Hao, did I hurt you?

111
00:12:45,639 --> 00:12:47,799
A real man doesn't mind a small injury.

112
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,679
This tiny scratch is nothing.

113
00:12:49,679 --> 00:12:52,240
Sister, don't worry.

114
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,960
Even if it's just a scrape,

115
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:57,640
I'll still be worried about you.

116
00:13:01,720 --> 00:13:04,480
Hao, does it still hurt now?

117
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:07,280
Sister, it doesn't hurt anymore.

118
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:15,999
Before you eat the beef tripe,

119
00:13:15,999 --> 00:13:17,559
take your medicine first.

120
00:13:22,799 --> 00:13:24,079
Open it.

121
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,319
There are a lot of gangsters outside
looking for you.

122
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:55,719
They said you are a traitor of Xiaoqi Hall.

123
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:59,040
Water.

124
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,839
- Why...
- Cigarettes.

125
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,160
No cigarettes.

126
00:14:35,159 --> 00:14:36,360
You're injured.

127
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,879
You can't smoke.

128
00:14:37,879 --> 00:14:39,559
Give me cigarettes.

129
00:14:42,039 --> 00:14:44,920
If you smoke, the medicine will be useless.

130
00:14:46,559 --> 00:14:48,160
Cigarettes.

131
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,800
No cigarettes.

132
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,800
It's bad for your health.

133
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,199
Recover.

134
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,599
Then leave.

135
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,319
Bro.

136
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:58,600
Bro.

137
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,760
Sister.

138
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,760
Sister.

139
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,159
Bro.

140
00:16:05,159 --> 00:16:08,120
Sister.

141
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:10,000
Bro. Sister.

142
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,000
How did you bleed so much?

143
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,160
Sister.

144
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:18,559
I'll get Dad.

145
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,719
Don't go.

146
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,400
I'm not leaving.

147
00:16:39,039 --> 00:16:40,640
I'll get you some water.

148
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,920
You were calling for

149
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:52,280
your brother and sister in your dream.

150
00:17:55,480 --> 00:17:57,480
Where are they?

151
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:59,319
They're dead.

152
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:11,119
Before, I lived in Xitou Lane.

153
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:19,520
When I was little,

154
00:18:22,079 --> 00:18:25,040
I was always thinking about
how to fill my stomach.

155
00:18:30,799 --> 00:18:32,480
My dad...

156
00:18:34,119 --> 00:18:36,040
He was a drug addict.

157
00:18:37,119 --> 00:18:38,880
He sniffed drugs.

158
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,519
He gambled.

159
00:18:40,519 --> 00:18:42,200
He drank heavily.

160
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,720
And my mom.

161
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:49,200
After giving birth to me,

162
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,000
she ran off with someone else.

163
00:18:53,039 --> 00:18:55,760
My sister is three years older than me.

164
00:18:57,160 --> 00:19:01,319
When other children were still clueless,

165
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,839
she already knew how to cook noodles
to comfort me.

166
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:11,919
My dad often beat us.

167
00:19:13,119 --> 00:19:15,399
He made us steal things for him.

168
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:20,960
If we couldn't steal,
he would beat us severely.

169
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:24,799
My sister always stood in front of me.

170
00:19:24,799 --> 00:19:27,040
She got beaten so badly
she couldn't get out of bed.

171
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:33,919
When I was ten,

172
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:41,599
my dad wanted to sell my sister
to be a prostitute.

173
00:19:43,799 --> 00:19:46,319
I grabbed her and ran away.

174
00:19:47,519 --> 00:19:49,280
He caught us and brought us back.

175
00:19:50,640 --> 00:19:53,119
It happened in an alley.

176
00:19:53,119 --> 00:19:55,040
He almost beat me to death.

177
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,919
Dad, stop hitting me.

178
00:20:07,079 --> 00:20:09,079
I'll kill you!

179
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,160
Get out of the way!

180
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,960
Move!

181
00:20:13,599 --> 00:20:14,880
Trying to run again?

182
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,519
You still want to run?

183
00:20:16,519 --> 00:20:17,960
Still running?

184
00:20:17,960 --> 00:20:19,319
I'll kill you!

185
00:20:20,999 --> 00:20:23,319
Long!

186
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:25,839
- Long!
- Hao, are you okay?

187
00:20:25,839 --> 00:20:28,200
Are you all right?

188
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:30,159
It was Qing Long who saved me.

189
00:20:31,079 --> 00:20:33,359
He just glanced at my dad.

190
00:20:33,359 --> 00:20:36,159
My dad immediately knelt and kowtowed to him.

191
00:20:38,799 --> 00:20:40,799
Let me treat you to some cake, okay?

192
00:20:40,799 --> 00:20:42,039
Long!

193
00:20:42,039 --> 00:20:44,399
Long, please spare me!

194
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,319
Eat up.

195
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:32,680
What are your names?

196
00:21:32,680 --> 00:21:34,119
I'm Xia Xiao Man.

197
00:21:34,119 --> 00:21:35,160
He's called Hao.

198
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,759
I'm not called Hao. He gave me that name.

199
00:21:36,759 --> 00:21:38,599
Be good, Hao.

200
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,799
If you dislike the name Hao so much,

201
00:21:41,799 --> 00:21:43,960
what name do you want?

202
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:46,400
Call me...

203
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:48,279
Call me Cake. I like cake.

204
00:21:48,279 --> 00:21:50,559
I'll be called Cake.

205
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:52,559
There are so many
delicious things in the world.

206
00:21:52,559 --> 00:21:54,039
But you just want to be named
after what you like to eat?

207
00:21:54,039 --> 00:21:55,599
I don't care, I don't care.

208
00:21:55,599 --> 00:21:56,920
I'll be called Cake.

209
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:59,279
Because I like cake.

210
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:00,359
How about this?

211
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:01,720
You are Liu Yi from now on.

212
00:22:01,720 --> 00:22:03,519
Every day, we'll celebrate Children's Day.

213
00:22:03,519 --> 00:22:05,319
And I'll treat you to cake every day, okay?

214
00:22:05,319 --> 00:22:07,159
Okay.

215
00:22:21,720 --> 00:22:23,200
He said...

216
00:22:23,839 --> 00:22:27,559
June 1st is Children's Day.

217
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,599
It belongs to me.

218
00:22:37,119 --> 00:22:39,639
It's a holiday for me and my sister.

219
00:22:49,839 --> 00:22:52,519
Later, we moved into the old house.

220
00:22:52,519 --> 00:22:54,000
Here.

221
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:55,799
Where do you want to reach by next year?

222
00:22:55,799 --> 00:22:58,880
This year, you're at this height.

223
00:22:58,880 --> 00:22:59,920
Here.

224
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:01,880
This tall?

225
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:04,319
Then I'll lift you to this height.

226
00:23:04,319 --> 00:23:07,200
Xiao Man wants to grow this tall.

227
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:10,040
Hao wants to be taller than you.

228
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:16,520
Bro knew that sister loved singing.

229
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:19,760
So, he sent her to study the arts.

230
00:23:21,200 --> 00:23:23,640
Knowing I liked to play with knives and sticks,

231
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:26,039
he found a master to teach me.

232
00:23:26,039 --> 00:23:28,159
When I grew up,

233
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:32,599
I begged him to let me
perform rituals in the hall

234
00:23:32,599 --> 00:23:34,639
and acknowledge him as the boss.

235
00:23:36,000 --> 00:23:38,480
In the first few years,

236
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,559
he wouldn't let me go out on tasks,

237
00:23:41,359 --> 00:23:43,200
saying I was too young.

238
00:23:43,200 --> 00:23:45,319
I could just stay by his side, that was enough.

239
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:50,760
When I was 18, he was ambushed.

240
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,759
He only had a few men with him.

241
00:23:54,759 --> 00:23:57,280
They were trapped in an alley.

242
00:23:59,519 --> 00:24:02,680
I went crazy, grabbing two knives,

243
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:04,639
and rushed in to save him.

244
00:24:33,079 --> 00:24:35,119
When I rescued him,

245
00:24:36,319 --> 00:24:38,079
he slapped me.

246
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,280
He said...

247
00:24:41,799 --> 00:24:43,599
even if he died,

248
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:48,159
he wouldn't want me
to risk my life to save him.

249
00:24:50,759 --> 00:24:52,680
After that,

250
00:24:53,319 --> 00:24:55,640
he told the elders,

251
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:58,599
that I should be promoted to Red Rod.

252
00:25:01,920 --> 00:25:03,760
That guy...

253
00:25:07,279 --> 00:25:09,839
He can be so contradictory.

254
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:17,879
My sister grew up.

255
00:25:20,359 --> 00:25:22,159
She got more and more beautiful.

256
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,440
Many bigshots took a liking to her.

257
00:25:27,079 --> 00:25:29,200
Qing Long tried to matchmake for her.

258
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,200
She didn't want any of them.

259
00:25:32,720 --> 00:25:34,040
One day,

260
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:36,839
she secretly told me

261
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,720
that she was in love with Qing Long.

262
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:44,399
She wanted to be Qing Long's woman.

263
00:25:48,319 --> 00:25:50,399
And shortly after,

264
00:25:51,680 --> 00:25:53,760
it would be my 20th birthday.

265
00:25:56,119 --> 00:25:58,399
Qing Long asked me what I wanted.

266
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:01,319
I...

267
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,960
I said...

268
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:11,280
I wanted my sister to be his wife.

269
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,040
Liu Yi.

270
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:34,280
Liu Yi.

271
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:37,159
Liu Yi.

272
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:40,000
Brother, you're here.

273
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,960
What's on your mind?

274
00:26:41,960 --> 00:26:43,280
Nothing.

275
00:26:44,160 --> 00:26:45,720
You're about to turn twenty.

276
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:47,680
What birthday gift do you want?

277
00:26:49,279 --> 00:26:50,680
Birthday?

278
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:56,279
Will you agree to anything I want?

279
00:26:56,279 --> 00:26:59,119
Of course. I care about you so much.

280
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:11,520
I want...

281
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:15,360
my sister to be your wife.

282
00:27:15,360 --> 00:27:17,839
I hope the three of us
can be like a real family.

283
00:27:17,839 --> 00:27:19,399
Forever together.

284
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:34,079
Okay.

285
00:27:35,039 --> 00:27:36,559
I promise you.

286
00:27:38,359 --> 00:27:41,000
Brother, I knew you were the best to me.

287
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:49,680
He agreed.

288
00:27:51,359 --> 00:27:53,280
He married my sister.

289
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:59,960
He even made me
a new pair of Qing Long dual blades.

290
00:28:00,599 --> 00:28:03,480
He also took me to meet the elders of the gang,

291
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:05,200
and told them

292
00:28:05,920 --> 00:28:08,280
that from now on, part of the gang's business

293
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:13,319
would gradually be handed to me to manage.

294
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,680
After that,

295
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,480
I became his right-hand man.

296
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:26,639
He was my boss.

297
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,800
And my sister became the missus boss.

298
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:44,879
I thought it would be like this forever.

299
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,280
That day,

300
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:58,359
I went to pick up my sister.

301
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,520
She jumped off the building.

302
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:12,639
And Bog Brother was killed, too...

303
00:29:20,559 --> 00:29:21,760
He was killed with...

304
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,520
the Qing Long dual blades

305
00:29:26,599 --> 00:29:28,440
he gave me.

306
00:29:29,519 --> 00:29:31,720
I failed to protect them.

307
00:29:32,759 --> 00:29:34,639
I failed.

308
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:39,200
I failed.

309
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:42,440
I failed.

310
00:29:52,039 --> 00:29:53,680
It was...

311
00:29:56,039 --> 00:29:59,119
that bastard Xu Ying.

312
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:03,159
He swapped my sister's medicine,

313
00:30:04,599 --> 00:30:06,960
causing her to relapse.

314
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:11,079
He killed my brother

315
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,359
and tried to frame me.

316
00:30:15,359 --> 00:30:16,879
The people chasing me

317
00:30:20,319 --> 00:30:22,520
were his men.

318
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:25,000
So...

319
00:30:26,559 --> 00:30:28,280
what do you plan to do now?

320
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:34,159
Kill him.

321
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:38,520
Avenge my brother

322
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:41,639
and my sister.

323
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:43,639
Take revenge.

324
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,280
Then what?

325
00:30:51,039 --> 00:30:52,440
Then...

326
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:56,599
You joined Xiaoqi Hall for Qing Long.

327
00:30:56,599 --> 00:30:58,839
You want to kill Xu Ying to take revenge.

328
00:31:00,640 --> 00:31:02,399
And after that?

329
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:13,000
Take care of the men Qing Long left behind.

330
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,559
And grow Xiaoqi Hall

331
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:24,919
into the biggest gang in the city.

332
00:32:33,424 --> 00:32:36,298
[Earn big money and buy a huge house for Dad]

333
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:41,359
Innocent student.

334
00:32:41,359 --> 00:32:43,599
Dad, I'll bring the medicine up.

335
00:32:43,599 --> 00:32:44,760
Okay.

336
00:33:16,839 --> 00:33:18,200
You walk so quietly.

337
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,000
You scared me to death.

338
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,839
Liu Yi.

339
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:25,839
Your eyelids seem a little swollen.

340
00:33:27,759 --> 00:33:29,639
Rub them with an egg.

341
00:33:38,799 --> 00:33:41,680
Don't get me wrong about last night.

342
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:43,720
I wasn't whining.

343
00:33:44,599 --> 00:33:45,760
I know.

344
00:33:50,359 --> 00:33:52,440
I'm not looking for your sympathy either.

345
00:33:53,519 --> 00:33:54,760
Okay.

346
00:33:56,599 --> 00:33:57,760
I...

347
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:01,599
I just wanted something to talk to.

348
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:04,919
There isn't even a single chicken here.

349
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:20,080
I want beef offal for breakfast.

350
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:23,840
Dad said you should
take this medicine before meals.

351
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,320
Here.

352
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,480
I won't take it. It smells awful.

353
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:29,360
- Beef offal.
- No.

354
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:31,000
Dad said the herbal medicine
must be taken before meals.

355
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,760
Three times a day.
Not a single dose can be skipped.

356
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,199
Three times?

357
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,880
That's enough to kill a rat!

358
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:36,880
Go away.

359
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:38,496
Throw it out!

360
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:43,280
Dad, someone's trying to
feed your medicine to the rats.

361
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,280
Who dares to mess with my medicine?

362
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:47,400
Him.

363
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:48,519
Gangsters have no education.

364
00:34:48,519 --> 00:34:49,559
Don't you have any education either?

365
00:34:49,559 --> 00:34:51,639
If the patient refuses the medicine,
can't you do something?

366
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:53,760
Why study so much?

367
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:54,800
When people get sick,

368
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:57,160
how can they get better without medicine?

369
00:34:58,039 --> 00:35:00,519
Bitter medicine is good for you.

370
00:35:00,519 --> 00:35:01,640
Chu San.

371
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:07,960
Chu San, don't laugh.

372
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,000
Hold his hands down.

373
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:10,640
Don't move.

374
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:18,760
Dad, you really know what to do.

375
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:20,920
How could a doctor be stumped by a patient?

376
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:23,560
Chu San, remember to change his dressing.

377
00:35:27,719 --> 00:35:29,239
You little punk.

378
00:35:29,239 --> 00:35:31,800
You better hope I never get better.

379
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:36,280
If I do get better,
you'll be the first on my hit list.

380
00:35:55,239 --> 00:35:56,760
It might hurt a little.

381
00:36:08,480 --> 00:36:10,039
It'll be over soon.

382
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:02,280
Liu Yi.

383
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,640
You need to sit up a bit.

384
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,479
Put more strength into it.

385
00:38:14,239 --> 00:38:15,439
What?

386
00:38:16,639 --> 00:38:18,280
I said, put more strength into it.

387
00:38:31,639 --> 00:38:33,120
What are you doing?

388
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,000
Wiping your butt.

389
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,760
Stick your butt out.

390
00:39:07,559 --> 00:39:09,359
Why are you gripping it so tightly?

391
00:39:10,559 --> 00:39:12,359
Do you want me to wipe the front for you?

392
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:15,680
I can do the front myself.

393
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,399
Do you want me to help?

394
00:39:39,519 --> 00:39:41,120
I can do it myself.

395
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,040
Chu San.

396
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:15,400
Time to get up.

397
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:17,360
I'm coming in.

398
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:20,000
Chu San, I made bone soup
for you and your friend.

399
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,280
Come down and drink it.

400
00:40:23,719 --> 00:40:25,640
Take it easy. Be careful.

401
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:32,400
Is this your friend?

402
00:40:32,400 --> 00:40:33,400
Very handsome.

403
00:40:33,400 --> 00:40:34,880
Hello.

404
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:37,199
Wash up and come down to eat.

405
00:40:37,199 --> 00:40:38,839
The food will get cold.

406
00:40:41,519 --> 00:40:43,239
Why did you kick me?

407
00:40:43,239 --> 00:40:44,839
Who kicked you?

408
00:40:52,800 --> 00:40:55,039
Fei, this is so delicious.

409
00:40:55,039 --> 00:40:58,239
I'm going to eat everything for breakfast.

410
00:40:58,239 --> 00:41:00,679
Fei, what you cooked is even better

411
00:41:00,679 --> 00:41:03,199
than what the most expensive chefs
in Harbor City make.

412
00:41:03,199 --> 00:41:06,800
Chu San, your friend really knows how to talk.

413
00:41:07,599 --> 00:41:10,000
Hey, come help a bit.

414
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:11,079
Okay, sure.

415
00:41:11,079 --> 00:41:13,080
I'll help.

416
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:16,120
I didn't expect you'd be so good at talking.

417
00:41:27,199 --> 00:41:28,519
Here, a snack for you.

418
00:41:28,519 --> 00:41:30,519
No way.

419
00:41:58,239 --> 00:42:00,280
Open the door!

420
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:02,119
Open up!

421
00:42:02,119 --> 00:42:05,000
- Hurry up.
- Who is it?

422
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:07,600
Why are you raising a fuss so early?

423
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,120
Where is he?

424
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:13,239
Sirs!

425
00:42:13,239 --> 00:42:15,480
Who are you looking for?

426
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:16,879
Sir!

427
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:20,359
Where is he? He's not here?

428
00:42:21,039 --> 00:42:22,039
Boss, only my son lives upstairs.

429
00:42:22,039 --> 00:42:24,200
Don't get in the way.

430
00:42:25,599 --> 00:42:26,960
Sir! Please!

431
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:29,720
Nobody else is upstairs. Just my son alone.

432
00:42:34,159 --> 00:42:36,200
Hey! Sirs!

433
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:41,480
Sirs, let's talk this out.

434
00:42:41,480 --> 00:42:43,879
My son has gone to school.

435
00:43:24,599 --> 00:43:26,159
Old man.

436
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:29,079
Your son is that university student
from the city fort, right?

437
00:43:29,079 --> 00:43:30,719
Yes, yes, yes.

438
00:43:30,719 --> 00:43:32,119
He's loved reading since he was a child.

439
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:33,639
Besides going to college,

440
00:43:33,639 --> 00:43:35,319
he hasn't really achieved much.

441
00:43:36,159 --> 00:43:38,239
Sirs, let me treat you to something.

442
00:43:38,239 --> 00:43:39,394
There's noise downstairs.

443
00:43:39,394 --> 00:43:40,975
Fuck!

444
00:43:49,920 --> 00:43:51,439
What are you doing?

445
00:43:54,639 --> 00:43:56,159
Nothing.

446
00:43:56,159 --> 00:43:57,159
Then why are you moving around?

447
00:43:57,159 --> 00:43:58,640
My back hurts.

448
00:44:02,639 --> 00:44:05,760
Sirs, I told you, no one's here.

449
00:44:09,559 --> 00:44:10,720
Go back.

450
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:29,959
Let's go.

451
00:44:34,119 --> 00:44:35,199
They must be around here.

452
00:44:35,199 --> 00:44:36,720
Search house by house.

453
00:44:40,679 --> 00:44:42,599
- Are you okay?
- Don't make a sound.

454
00:44:42,599 --> 00:44:43,919
Quiet.

455
00:44:46,199 --> 00:44:47,840
Move.

456
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:48,919
Okay.

457
00:44:59,240 --> 00:45:00,279
Are you kidding me?

458
00:45:00,279 --> 00:45:01,800
Running away with that crappy backpack?

459
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:02,800
I have my final exam today.

460
00:45:02,800 --> 00:45:04,399
I'm afraid I won't make it in time.

461
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:08,600
Your wound has reopened.

462
00:45:12,400 --> 00:45:14,600
Xia Liu Yi, I...

463
00:45:15,239 --> 00:45:17,159
Don't call me that.

464
00:45:17,159 --> 00:45:18,439
It's Big Bro Liu Yi.

465
00:45:19,079 --> 00:45:20,959
I'm not your underling.

466
00:45:22,599 --> 00:45:23,840
So many people begged to be my underling,

467
00:45:23,840 --> 00:45:25,280
and they couldn't.

468
00:45:25,280 --> 00:45:26,599
Plus, I'm three years older than you.

469
00:45:26,599 --> 00:45:28,399
That clearly makes me your big brother.

470
00:45:34,519 --> 00:45:35,959
Did you grow taller?

471
00:45:37,639 --> 00:45:39,840
I've always been taller than you.

472
00:45:39,840 --> 00:45:41,999
Just not as strong as you.

473
00:45:43,159 --> 00:45:44,519
Take off the clothes.

474
00:45:47,480 --> 00:45:48,639
Take whose off?

475
00:45:48,639 --> 00:45:50,039
Ours.

476
00:45:50,039 --> 00:45:52,519
- I...
- Help me stop the bleeding.

477
00:45:54,559 --> 00:45:57,600
Also, help me with something.

478
00:45:58,800 --> 00:46:00,359
I can help you.

479
00:46:00,960 --> 00:46:02,320
But I'm not your underling.

480
00:46:02,320 --> 00:46:03,760
Shut up.

481
00:46:04,514 --> 00:46:11,017
[Ganglong Walled City]

482
00:46:31,599 --> 00:46:33,199
Xia Liu Yi's knife?

483
00:46:33,199 --> 00:46:35,039
Why is it here?

484
00:46:35,039 --> 00:46:37,679
I don't know. I know nothing.

485
00:46:37,679 --> 00:46:39,159
Don't know?

486
00:46:39,159 --> 00:46:40,760
Tell me, where is Xia Liu Yi?

487
00:46:40,760 --> 00:46:42,119
I-I don't know.

488
00:46:42,119 --> 00:46:43,919
Do you want to be stabbed?

489
00:46:48,000 --> 00:46:51,239
He forced me to throw this knife away.

490
00:46:51,239 --> 00:46:54,360
He said to wait for me at Xiaoqi Studio.

491
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:56,880
You better not play tricks.

492
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:58,079
Go tell Brother Xu.

493
00:46:58,079 --> 00:46:59,240
Tell him Xia Liu Yi has been found.

494
00:46:59,240 --> 00:47:00,279
At Xiaoqi Studio.

495
00:47:00,279 --> 00:47:01,800
Then what about this kid?

496
00:47:01,800 --> 00:47:04,080
I've told you everything.

497
00:47:05,119 --> 00:47:07,960
Can you let me go?

498
00:47:07,960 --> 00:47:09,519
What?

499
00:47:09,519 --> 00:47:10,800
Take him with you.

500
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:13,039
If we fail, at least we have him
to report to Brother Xu.

501
00:47:13,039 --> 00:47:14,360
- Come on.
- Get moving.

502
00:47:14,360 --> 00:47:15,560
Move.

503
00:47:16,519 --> 00:47:17,680
Walk.

504
00:47:18,599 --> 00:47:19,760
Hurry up.

505
00:48:24,159 --> 00:48:27,359
Qing Long really hid the ledgers with you.

506
00:48:30,639 --> 00:48:33,159
You had a student help you
get rid of the bloody clothes,

507
00:48:33,159 --> 00:48:35,400
making me think you left the city.

508
00:48:35,400 --> 00:48:38,760
Xia Liu Yi, how could you be so stupid?

